PostScript-Simple-Table version 1.00
=============================

Adds easy table creation to PostScript::Simple.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  PostScript::Simple
  PostScript::Metrics

